  "body": "When creating a new account or opening the app for the very first time, the QML settings do not save.\n\nSteps:\n1. Create a new account\n2. Go to profile\n3. change any setting, like activating communities and the wallet in Advanced\n4. Close the app\n5. Re-open and login\n-> Communities and Wallet are no longer enabled.\n\nThe save does happen on another close though\n\nCould be related to the QML settings being saved in a file with the account's address and maybe we don't set that address/file correctly on first load.",
